<p><strong>How to use the crafting calculator:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Print out one page of the individual pricing calculator for each produc=
t (I recommend you aim for 100 listings to really establish a solid Etsy sh=
op).</li>
<li>Print 1 table for every ten products/every shop section, or however you=
 want to organize it.</li>
<li>Place them in a binder in or out of sheet protectors.</li>
<li>Add a brainstorming page and a note page for each table page.</li>
<li>Add dividers for each section/set of ten.</li>
<li>Keep this binder handy. Check in on sales monthly, see how to adjust it=
, how to plan new seasonal goods.</li>
</ul>
